about it in Scientific American.

1020
01:24:54,756 --> 01:24:55,839
Scientific American?

1021
01:24:56,007 --> 01:24:58,550
Look, I just want to say,
no hard feelings, okay?

1022
01:24:58,718 --> 01:25:01,095
