and expansion thing.

1023
01:25:01,262 --> 01:25:03,764
So I'm actually looking
for my own building anyway.

1024
01:25:03,932 --> 01:25:06,767
How exactly
are you going to do that, Trevor?

1025
01:25:07,644 --> 01:25:10,020
Well, let's just say
I fell into a small fortune.

1026
